rehab:exercises.title: Core workout
rehab:exercises.description: 12 minute boxing timer routine. Fast paced abs, hips, and back.

rehab:exercises.title: Smith - Squat
rehab:exercises.description: Using a smith machine, injured leg is directly underneath. Other leg supports through the challenging ranges.

rehab:exercises.title: Smith - Forward lunge
rehab:exercises.description: Using the smith machine, injured leg in front, forward lunge.

rehab:exercises.title: Quarter wall sit
rehab:exercises.description: Wall sit only about 1/4 depth to prevent pain. Balancing against the wall on injured leg

rehab:exercises.title: Bounding
rehab:exercises.description: Forward, reverse, lateral skips and hops

rehab:exercises.title: Leg extension
rehab:exercises.description: Seated single leg extension with ankle weights. Lift up squeeze at the top, slow on the way down.

rehab:exercises.title: Straight leg raise
rehab:exercises.description: Laying on back, single straight leg raise with ankle weights.

rehab:exercises.title: Buso lunges
rehab:exercises.description: Side, back, and curtsey lunges with injured leg on the buso ball

rehab:exercises.title: Buso single leg balance
rehab:exercises.description: Balance on Buso ball with single leg slightly bent

rehab:exercises.title: Mobility stretch
rehab:exercises.description: General stretch to get loose and increase mobility and blood flow.

rehab:exercises.title: Heel raises
rehab:exercises.description: Standing explosive heel raise on to toes both feet

rehab:exercises.title: Slide board sprints
rehab:exercises.description: Slide board 45 seconds on with 15 seconds off

rehab:exercises.title: Back extension
rehab:exercises.description: Bend down and lean forward on stand. Lift back and squeeze at top.

rehab:entries.notes: Mostly took it easy. I felt really sore and had low energy.
Was busy. Didn't have time to workout in the morning.  Knee was hurting from the walk on Friday.

Definitely favoring my left during the smith squats. Upped the weight from last week. The lunge bothered my left knee. Skipped that today.  Tried 80lb on the leg press. Hurt too much. Went back to 70. Could not do bounding. Too painful
Knee felt great today. Bounding felt totally fine. No issues with anything. Full ROM
